suggest.api-platform/doctrine-odm: To support MongoDB. Only versions 4.0 and later are supported.
suggest.ocramius/package-versions: To display the API Platform's version in the debug bar.
suggest.phpstan/phpdoc-parser: To support extracting metadata from PHPDoc.
suggest.symfony/cache: To have metadata caching when using Symfony integration.
suggest.symfony/expression-language: To use authorization and mercure advanced features.
suggest.symfony/http-client: To use the HTTP cache invalidation system.
suggest.symfony/twig-bundle: To use the Swagger UI integration.
suggest.symfony/messenger: To support messenger integration and asynchronous Mercure updates.
